import React from 'react'
import {Conatiner, Row, Col} from 'react-bootstrap'
import Sidebar from '../Components/Sidebar'
import MessageForm from '../Components/MessageForm'

const Chat = () => {
    return (
        <Conatiner>
            <Row>
                <Col md={4}>
                    <Sidebar />
                </Col>
                <Col m={8}>
                    <MessageForm />
                </Col>
            </Row>
        </Conatiner>
    )
}

export default Chat
